            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3ETrials%20and%20troubles%20tend%20to%20make%20us%20fearful.%20Instead%20of%20feeling%20stout%20and%20bold%2C%20we%20feel%20stooped%20and%20cold!%20However%2C%20Zephaniah%203%3A17%20reminds%20us%2C%20%22For%20the%20Lord%20your%20God%20has%20arrived%20to%20live%20among%20you.%20He%20is%20a%20mighty%20savior.%20He%20will%20rejoice%20over%20you%20with%20great%20gladness.%20With%20his%20love%2C%20he%20will%20calm%20all%20your%20fears.%20He%20will%20exult%20over%20you%20by%20singing%20a%20happy%20song.%22%20This%20is%20your%20first%20secret%20to%20recovery%3A%20God%20is%20with%20you!%20Having%20Him%20on%20your%20side%20is%20like%20having%20the%20United%20States%20Army%20on%20your%20side%20in%20a%20skirmish%20with%20a%20Boy%20Scout%20troop!%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ENext%2C%20He%20will%20rejoice%20over%20you%20with%20gladness.%20All%20His%20attention%20and%20loving%20affection%20is%20directed%20toward%20you%20in%20the%20same%20way%20a%20father%20directs%20his%20attention%20toward%20his%20son.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThen%2C%20He%20will%20calm%20all%20your%20fears.%20Your%20fearful%2C%20timid%20whining%20is%20for%20nothing%2C%20because%20perfect%20love%20casts%20out%20fear%20(1%20John%204%3A18).%20You%20can%20rest%20contented%20and%20safe%20in%20His%20arms.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EFinally%2C%20He%20exults%20over%20you%20by%20singing%20a%20happy%20song.%20This%20picture%20is%20like%20that%20of%20a%20parent%20holding%20a%20child%20and%20singing%20to%20him%20in%20his%20darkest%20hour.%20Can%20you%20imagine%20God%20singing%20songs%20of%20deliverance%20over%20you%3F%20What%20enemy%20has%20a%20chance%20against%20such%20odds%3F%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EBe%20bold%20and%20strong%2C%20for%20your%20Father%20is%20on%20the%20scene.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
