            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EZephaniah%201%3A1-3%3A20%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22zeph_1_1%22%20bk%3D%22zeph%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EZephaniah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20gave%20this%20message%20to%20Zephaniah%20when%20Josiah%20son%20of%20Amon%20was%20king%20of%20Judah.%20Zephaniah%20was%20the%20son%20of%20Cushi%2C%20son%20of%20Gedaliah%2C%20son%20of%20Amariah%2C%20son%20of%20Hezekiah.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22zeph_1_2%22%20bk%3D%22zeph%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EComing%20Judgment%20against%20Judah%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20will%20sweep%20away%20everything%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efrom%20the%20face%20of%20the%20earth%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20says%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22zeph_1_3%22%20bk%3D%22zeph%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20will%20sweep%20away%20people%20and%20animals%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EI%20will%20sweep%20away%20the%20birds%20of%20the%20sky%20and%20the%20fish%20in%20the%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EI%20will%20reduce%20the%20wicked%20to%20heaps%20of%20rubble%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A3%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20meaning%20of%20the%20Hebrew%20is%20uncertain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20I%20will%20wipe%20humanity%20from%20the%20face%20of%20the%20earth%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20says%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22zeph_1_4%22%20bk%3D%22zeph%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20will%20crush%20Judah%20and%20Jerusalem%20with%20my%20fist%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20destroy%20every%20last%20trace%20of%20their%20Baal%20worship.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EI%20will%20put%20an%20end%20to%20all%20the%20idolatrous%20priests%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eso%20that%20even%20the%20memory%20of%20them%20will%20disappear.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22zeph_1_5%22%20bk%3D%22zeph%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20they%20go%20up%20to%20their%20roofs%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20bow%20down%20to%20the%20sun%2C%20moon%2C%20and%20stars.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThey%20claim%20to%20follow%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ebut%20then%20they%20worship%20Molech%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A5%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EMalcam%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20variant%20spelling%20of%20Molech%3B%20or%20it%20could%20possibly%20mean%20%3Cem%3Etheir%20king.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22zeph_1_6%22%20bk%3D%22zeph%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20I%20will%20destroy%20those%20who%20used%20to%20worship%20me%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ebut%20now%20no%20longer%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThey%20no%20longer%20ask%20for%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20guidance%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eor%20seek%20my%20blessings.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22zeph_1_7%22%20bk%3D%22zeph%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EStand%20in%20silence%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efor%20the%20awesome%20day%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20judgment%20is%20near.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20prepared%20his%20people%20for%20a%20great%20slaughter%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20has%20chosen%20their%20executioners.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A7%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ehas%20prepared%20a%20sacrifice%20and%20sanctified%20his%20guests.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22zeph_1_8%22%20bk%3D%22zeph%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BOn%20that%20day%20of%20judgment%2C%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Esays%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20will%20punish%20the%20leaders%20and%20princes%20of%20Judah%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20all%20those%20following%20pagan%20customs.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22zeph_1_9%22%20bk%3D%22zeph%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EYes%2C%20I%20will%20punish%20those%20who%20participate%20in%20pagan%20worship%20ceremon